jobs.prompt:
Read `03_outreach_angles.json`. For each record, POST to `/crm/v3/objects/notes` via the praxis_integration `create_note` capability with:

```json
{
  "properties": {
    "hs_note_body": "<angle_markdown>",
    "hs_timestamp": "<epoch_ms_now>"
  },
  "associations": [
    {"to":{"id":"<deal_id>"},"types":[{"associationCategory":"HUBSPOT_DEFINED","associationTypeId":214}]},
    {"to":{"id":"<contact_id>"},"types":[{"associationCategory":"HUBSPOT_DEFINED","associationTypeId":202}]}
  ]
}
```

Call it with `praxis workflow tools call praxis_integration --input-json '{"action":"call","integration_id":"hubspot","integration_action":"create_note","args":{...}}' --yes`.

Capture the returned note id for each call and write the pairs to `artifacts/hubspot_enrichment_20260418/04_note_ids.json` as `[{deal_id, contact_id, note_id, hubspot_status}]`. On any failure, record the error body in the same row (`hubspot_status:"failed"`, `error_detail`) — do NOT abort the whole run for a single failed note.
